720931f-a.title: Manhattan: Lexington Avenue - 26th Street (East)
720931f-a.text:
Lexington Avenue, north from East 26th Street,
showing an early view of this arterial thoroughfare.
Note the street-cartracks. These were removed (by
the C. W. A.) and service continued by busses.
April 13, 1924
Standard Photographic Service
Gift of Borough President of Manhattan
